cal strengths and stress handling outweigh the interpersonal concerns, which appear less likely to compromise flight safety than the more severe teamwork or health issues seen in the other candidates.\nTherefore, I continue to support **Candidate\u202fB** as the best overall fit for the long\u2011distance pilot role.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
